你怎么知道你不会被卖家骗？

137
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:11,080
Well, the website handles a point system where if the seller does something wrong, people
嗯，网站有一个积分系统，如果卖家做错了什么，人们

138
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,640
comment negatively.
会给出负面评论。

139
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:15,160
And then you know that he or she may not be trustworthy.
然后你就知道他或她可能不值得信赖。

140
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:17,680
Wow, that sounds pretty safe.
哇，听起来挺安全的。

141
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,920
So how do you pay?
那你怎么付款呢？

142
